-- Euro Reverses Advance Versus Dollar; Weakens 0.1% to $1.2457
-- B y   D a v i d   G o o d m a n
-- 2012-06-28T07:59:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/euro-reverses-advance-versus-dollar-weakens-0-1-to-1-2457.html
The euro reversed an advance against
the dollar and extended a decline against the yen.  The 17-nation shared currency was 0.1 percent weaker at
$1.2457 as of 8:58 a.m. London time, after earlier climbing as
much as 0.5 percent to $1.2524. It declined 0.5 percent to 98.95
yen.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Goodman in London at 
